text: Karel Janež (born 22 January 1914, date of death unknown) was a Slovenian gymnast. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Slovenian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ljubljana
